<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms taste of acid in mouth, unusual taste in mouth and white patches on tongue including Heartburn/GERD, Thrush (infants and children), and Medication reaction or side-effect.</p>
